opinion.opinion_text:
ORDER GRANTING MOTION TO DISMISS APPEAL Upon consideration of appellant's motion to dismiss appeal, the papers in support and the record,
IT IS HEREBY ORDERED that the motion to dismiss appeal is granted. This appeal is dismissed. The parties shall bear their own costs and fees.
